### Base Template

# This template covers universal patterns only. Language and framework-specific
# patterns should be appended to this template based on specific project needs:
# https://github.com/github/gitignore

# Agent and Developer Temporary Files
.tmp/

# Environment and Secrets
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# OS-Generated Files
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
.DS_Store
._*

# Editor and IDE
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.idea/
*.iml
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/extensions.json
*.code-workspace

# Build Artifacts
dist/
build/
out/
